		<header class="header">
			
			<h1 class="title" align="left">
				梦里水乡，醉是涵江，那些最想留住的记忆~
			</h1>
			<div class="desc">
				<img src="//om.gtimg.cn/om/om_3.0/h5_detail/images/logo_qiehao.png" class="logo">
				<span class="author">莆田旅游</span>
				<span class="date">2019-12-10</span>
			</div>
			
		</header>
		<section class="article">
			

			

			
		
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10796386110/0" width="100%" style="display:block;"
					data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_match/0/10796386110/0">
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					
						<p>萝苜田，又叫萝田，很美丽的地名。位于涵江特色红砖厝建筑群内，地名的缘由是此地人家喜欢在田地种满萝卜，甚是有趣。当地的建筑风格是典型的涵江红砖大厝，最明显的特征是“红砖”和“燕尾脊”。爬上高处俯瞰整个红色建筑群，别有感觉。</p>
					
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008768/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008768/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008769/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008769/641">
							
						
						
					</div>
				
			
				
					<div align="center" class="img-mod">
						
							
								<img src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008771/641" width="100%" style="display:block;"
								data-width="400" data-height="263" preview-src="http://inews.gtimg.com/newsapp_bt/0/8508008771/641">
							
						
						
